{"tid":567094,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"孤兒瘋人院","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T14:13:26.000Z","uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b968c97d727ae74c552e1422c69e55733067e478","tid":567094,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"專收集一堆說話太瘋癲而被踢的孤兒，隨意傾談你既所思所想，但以下人士請勿內進<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 23歲以下人士<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵食人士即踢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗公麻煩走啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 娘娘行遠啲呀<br />\n<br />\n我地谷內已有專屬狗公、娘娘、搵食人士，佢地會不斷監察，以防有人威脅到佢地既地位。<br />\n每個月會清一次深潛人士，拒絕cdrom，大家有心想傾計先入，谷內有來自各行各業既人，想傾乜都可以，只怕你開唔到題。<br />\n<br />\n有心入谷既朋友可以pm佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n@Icyyyyyy <br />\n或<br />\n@Ifidrunktoday"}]}